  "remarks": "\nKhin Phyu Win is an involved person under The Myanmar (Sanctions) Regulations 2021. In her role as current Director and shareholder of Shoon Energy Pte Limited, Khin Phyu Win has been \nprofiting financially from activity which represses the civilian population in Myanmar, namely through the supply of aviation fuel. \n",
